metadata.name: Silence Teaches
metadata.description:
As you know, the sniper is one of the key elements that can be positioned in places you cannot see on the battlefields and perform the most accurate shot in line with a certain wisdom. The individuals to whom the sniper is attributed in this collection are real individuals that the Masculine society ignores
